column15: Player can die because of other sprite
column16: Goal to survive for time period

column22: if sprites are bombers AND spawnorientation=LEFT, then spread them vertically, close to the right of the screen
if sprites are bombers AND spawnorientation=RIGHT, then spread them vertically, close to the left of the screen
if sprites are bombers AND spawnorientation=UP, then spread them horizontally, close to the bottom of the screen
if sprites are bombers AND spawnorientation=DOWN, then spread them horizontally, close to the top of the screen
if SpawnPoint then place it to the side opposite to the orientation of the stype
if no EOS interaction is defined then put walls around the edges of the level
if a sprite x has an interaction defined with a Missle, then put sprite x orthogonal to this Missle.
